{
  "stem": "21788.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I went in there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It had a different name-- Schmidt, or something.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, the name of the bakery was, I found out later, [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went into this bakery, and I said to the lady behind the counter, was this the bakery [GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And right away she kind of became very standoffish and said, why do you want to know?",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Bruckenstrasse was in the Russian zone, and after the Russian zone became now just Berlin again, there is lots of people that have owned houses before the reunification, and there's a lot of trouble going on.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So she like, who are you?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why do you want to know?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I said to her, the last time I came to your bakery was 50 years ago.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I lived across the street.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I emigrated to China, and then to the United States.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, I see.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And then she became friendly and she said, no, no, this was not the bakery [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It was the bakery [GERMAN].",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she says, it's about time that you come back and buy some cake, which I did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So anyway, right next to the bakery [GERMAN] was a hardware store.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the hardware store was owned by a [?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Fuchs ?], F-U-X, or maybe C-H.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He was Jewish.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Kristallnacht, by 11 o'clock at night, 12 o'clock at night-- I don't remember what time it actually was-- the Nazis came, the Hitler Youth came-- the SS actually is what it was-- and smashed in the store.",
      "word_count": 37
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And, of course, looted it, by the way, too.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now could you see this from your house?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, yes, yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we saw it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We saw it right from-- from our window.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "As far as emotion is concerned, I don't think I grasped the significance on it.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
